    {
      "parameters": {
        "html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"id\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\"/>\n  <title>Laporan Strategi Bisnis & Intelijen Kompetitif</title>\n\n  <style>\n    :root {\n      --orange: #D85A30;\n      --blue: #185FA5;\n      --blue-light: #378ADD;\n      --gray-bg: #f8f9fa;\n      --text-dark: #333;\n      --text-light: #6c757d;\n    }\n\n    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }\n\n    body {\n      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\n      line-height: 1.6;\n      color: var(--text-dark);\n      background: #ffffff;\n    }\n\n    .container { max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 24px; }\n\n    header {\n      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--blue), var(--blue-light));\n      color: white;\n      padding: 48px 24px;\n      text-align: center;\n      border-radius: 0 0 14px 14px;\n    }\n\n    header h1 { font-size: 28px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 10px; }\n    header p { font-size: 15px; opacity: 0.95; }\n\n    .badge {\n      display: inline-block;\n      margin-top: 12px;\n      background: var(--orange);\n      padding: 6px 14px;\n      border-radius: 20px;\n      font-size: 13px;\n      font-weight: bold;\n    }\n\n    section {\n      background: #ffffff;\n      margin: 32px 0;\n      padding: 28px;\n      border-radius: 12px;\n      border: 1px solid #eee;\n    }\n\n    h2 {\n      font-size: 22px;\n      color: var(--blue);\n      margin-bottom: 18px;\n      padding-bottom: 8px;\n      border-bottom: 2px solid var(--orange);\n    }\n\n    h3 { font-size: 18px; color: var(--blue); margin: 18px 0 10px; }\n    p { margin-bottom: 12px; }\n    ul, ol { margin-left: 22px; }\n    li { margin-bottom: 10px; }\n\n    .highlight {\n      background: #fff4e6;\n      padding: 2px 6px;\n      border-radius: 4px;\n      font-weight: bold;\n      color: #d35400;\n    }\n\n    table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-top: 16px; }\n\n    th {\n      background: var(--blue);\n      color: white;\n      padding: 12px;\n      font-size: 14px;\n    }\n\n    td {\n      padding: 12px;\n      border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;\n      font-size: 14px;\n      vertical-align: top;\n    }\n\n    .brand-bisa { background: #fff7f1; }\n    .brand-nf   { background: #f1f6ff; }\n    .brand-vinix { background: #f5f5f5; }\n\n    .score-bisa  { color: var(--orange); font-weight: bold; }\n    .score-nf    { color: var(--blue);   font-weight: bold; }\n    .score-vinix { color: #888780;       font-weight: bold; }\n\n    .bar {\n      height: 18px;\n      border-radius: 10px;\n      margin: 6px 0 14px;\n      background: #ddd;\n      overflow: hidden;\n    }\n\n    .bar span { display: block; height: 100%; }\n    .bar-bisa  span { width: 53.3%; background: var(--orange); }\n    .bar-nf    span { width: 46.7%; background: var(--blue); }\n    .bar-vinix span { width: 0%;    background: #888780; }\n\n    .note {\n      font-size: 13px;\n      color: #6c757d;\n      background: #f8f9fa;\n      border-left: 4px solid #888780;\n      padding: 10px 14px;\n      border-radius: 4px;\n      margin-top: 8px;\n    }\n\n    footer {\n      margin-top: 40px;\n      text-align: center;\n      font-size: 13px;\n      color: var(--text-light);\n    }\n\n    @media print { section { page-break-inside: avoid; } }\n  </style>\n</head>\n\n<body>\n\n<header>\n  <div class=\"container\">\n    <h1>📊 Laporan Strategi Bisnis & Intelijen Kompetitif</h1>\n    <p>Analisis Share of Voice (SoV) & Reputasi Digital</p>\n    <div class=\"badge\">📅 07 Januari 2026</div>\n  </div>\n</header>\n\n<div class=\"container\">\n\n  <section>\n    <h2>📌 Ringkasan Eksekutif</h2>\n    <p>\n      Dalam percakapan digital terbatas (<strong>15 mention</strong>),\n      <span class=\"highlight\">BISA AI</span> unggul tipis dengan\n      <strong>53.3% Share of Voice</strong>, sementara\n      <strong>NF Academy</strong> berada di <strong>46.7%</strong>.\n      <strong>Vinix 7</strong> tidak ditemukan dalam periode analisis ini.\n    </p>\n\n    <p><strong>BISA AI (53.3%)</strong></p>\n    <div class=\"bar bar-bisa\"><span></span></div>\n\n    <p><strong>NF Academy (46.7%)</strong></p>\n    <div class=\"bar bar-nf\"><span></span></div>\n\n    <p><strong>Vinix 7 (0% — tidak terdeteksi)</strong></p>\n    <div class=\"bar bar-vinix\"><span></span></div>\n    <div class=\"note\">\n      ⚠️ Vinix 7 tidak ditemukan dalam 15 mention yang dianalisis pada periode Januari 2026.\n      Ini bukan error data, melainkan brand tersebut memang tidak aktif atau tidak terpantau\n      di platform yang dimonitor. Perlu investigasi lebih lanjut.\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section>\n    <h2>📢 Analisis Share of Voice</h2>\n\n    <h3>🤖 BISA AI</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Fokus topikal AI & Data Science</li>\n      <li>Promosi agresif dan edukatif</li>\n      <li>Akses kursus gratis + sertifikasi</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h3>🎓 NF Academy</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Konten dominan profil statis</li>\n      <li>Minim diskusi & CTA viral</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h3>🔍 Vinix 7</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Tidak ditemukan mention dalam periode analisis (Jan 2026)</li>\n      <li>Kemungkinan aktif di platform yang tidak masuk dalam scope monitoring</li>\n      <li>Perlu perluasan scope pencarian untuk periode berikutnya</li>\n    </ul>\n  </section>\n\n  <section>\n    <h2>⭐ Skor Reputasi</h2>\n    <table>\n      <tr>\n        <th>Brand</th>\n        <th>Skor</th>\n        <th>Kelebihan</th>\n        <th>Kelemahan</th>\n      </tr>\n      <tr class=\"brand-bisa\">\n        <td><strong>BISA AI</strong></td>\n        <td class=\"score-bisa\">8.0 / 10</td>\n        <td>Relevan, gratis, online</td>\n        <td>Branding generik</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr class=\"brand-nf\">\n        <td><strong>NF Academy</strong></td>\n        <td class=\"score-nf\">6.5 / 10</td>\n        <td>Lokasi fisik, B2B</td>\n        <td>Konten kaku</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr class=\"brand-vinix\">\n        <td><strong>Vinix 7</strong></td>\n        <td class=\"score-vinix\">N/A</td>\n        <td>—</td>\n        <td>Tidak ada data mention; tidak dapat dinilai pada periode ini</td>\n      </tr>\n    </table>\n  </section>\n\n  <section>\n    <h2>💡 Strategi Rekomendasi untuk NF Academy</h2>\n    <ol>\n      <li>Aktifkan konten sosial & instruktur</li>\n      <li>Tonjolkan keunggulan kelas tatap muka</li>\n      <li>Gunakan promosi berbasis hasil nyata</li>\n    </ol>\n  </section>\n\n  <footer>\n    <p>© 2026 — Laporan Strategi Bisnis & Intelijen Kompetitif</p>\n    <p>Data publik & analisis sosial media (Jan 2026)</p>\n  </footer>\n\n</div>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"
      },
